race.description: Futurity Pastoral Showcase Baradine Cup Hcp
race.comment: SLUSH FUND (4) rewarded for his consistency when taken to the front for a fighting head win over 1400m at Coonamble. Zoe Hunt retains the ride and can handle the weight rise. Solid top three player. THE IMPECKABLE (9) struggled to see the mile out when shuffled back early for a plodding fourth over 1600m at Coonamble. Senior rider goes on and comes here in peak condition.  NIGHT FIGHTER (13) far from disgraced when sent to town for a handy seventh over 1500m at Rosehill in Highway class. Maps well and no shock to see him find the winners' list. DAWN COUNTY (1) chasing his fourth win from his last five starts and Stiff's 3kg claim keeps him in contention. Came with a well-timed run when saluting over the 1450m at Muswellbrook. Going too well to ignore.MRS BULL (8) tenacious mare who's returned to form at her last two outings. Gets the right run.
